These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, fantasy, time-travel, horror
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, skateboard, subway, van
1. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
2. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
3. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
5. the person driving the van is between the person driving the skateboard and the person driving the subway##2
6. the person watching horror movies is the person driving the tram##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | spy     | time-travel | fantasy |
| Transport     | tram     | subway | van  | skateboard      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, salsa, punk, folk
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, car, subway, jet-ski
1. the fan of salsa is on the left of the person driving the car##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fan of folk is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the car##1
5. the fan of punk is on the far right##1
6. the person driving the ship is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | disco | salsa    | folk     | punk  |
| Transport     | ship    | subway | car | jet-ski |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, metal, techno, hip-hop
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, frog, hedgehog, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
2. the fan of metal is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the fan of trance##3
5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | metal   | techno   | trance  | hip-hop |
| Pet           | frog | guinea-pig | hedgehog | goldfish  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, cooking, baking, sudoku
There are 4 different nationalities: french, russian, mexican, british
1. the british is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is between the person who's hobby is writing and the mexican##2
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
4. the mexican is on the left or right of the british##3
5. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
6. the french is on the right of the russian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | cooking | writing | sudoku | baking  |
| Nationality   | russian  | french   | british  | mexican |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, sprite, water
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, sudoku, board-games, skydiving
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
4. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | almond-milk    | cola   | sprite | water    |
| Hobby      | sudoku | reading | board-games       | skydiving |

