.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, iced-tea, tea, milk
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, motorbike, scooter, bike
1. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
2. the person driving the scooter is between the person driving the bike and the person drinking tea##2
3. the person driving the skateboard is between the person driving the scooter and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
4. the person driving the bike is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate | tea | milk | iced-tea |
| Transport   | motorbike | skateboard  | scooter    | bike  |

