2. the mexican is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
4. the spanish is between the dutch and the indonesian##2
5. the person driving the tram is the person driving the tram##1
6. the person driving the tram is between the person driving the boat and the indonesian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2   |   3    |     4      |
| Nationality   | mexican | indonesian | spanish | dutch     |
| Transport     | subway | jet-ski  | tram   | boat |

