.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, hiking, photography, card-games
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, romance, adventure, thriller
1. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
2. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person watching romance movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
6. the person watching romance movies is on the left or right of the person watching adventure movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Hobby         | card-games | photography | singing | hiking   |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | adventure | drama      | thriller |

