.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-9::.
4 different pets are kept: dog, frog, rabbit, goldfish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, surfing, baseball, water-polo
1. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is the owner of the goldfish##1
4. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
5. the owner of the dog is on the far left or far right##3
6. the owner of the frog is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person who's sport is climbing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Pet     | dog | frog   | rabbit      | goldfish      |
| Sport   | surfing     | baseball | climbing | water-polo |

