.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, d&b, trance, dubstep
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, dutch, thai, mexican
1. the indonesian is on the right of the dutch##1
2. the fan of trance is between the mexican and the dutch##2
3. the fan of d&b is the dutch##1
4. the thai is on the left of the dutch##1
5. the fan of dubstep is on the left or right of the indonesian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | d&b | trance      | dubstep   |
| Nationality   | thai  | dutch    | indonesian | mexican |

