3. the person driving the train is the person who's hobby is photography##1
4. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
5. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##3
6. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby       | woodworking | photography | rock-climbing    | baking      |
| Transport   | helicopter       | train       | roller | ship |

