.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-13::.
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, colombian, japanese, pakistani
4 different pets are kept: ferret, cat, pony, chinchilla
1. the colombian is on the far right##1
2. the indonesian is the indonesian##1
3. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
4. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the colombian##3
5. the japanese is on the left or right of the pakistani##3
6. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the pakistani##3
7. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Nationality   | indonesian | japanese  | pakistani | colombian |
| Pet           | pony     | chinchilla | ferret    | cat     |

