.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-14::.
There 4 different types of food: grapes, apple, apricot, grapefruit
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, architect, engineer, security-guard
1. the person eating grapefruit is on the left or right of the architect##3
2. the architect is on the right of the engineer##1
3. the person eating apple is on the left of the fisherman##1
4. the architect is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating apricot is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Food   | apple  | grapes | grapefruit  | apricot      |
| Job    | security-guard | fisherman | engineer | architect |

