5. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the fan of ambient##3
6. the fan of d&b is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
7. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the fan of house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | board-games | fishing | chess | cooking |
| Music-Genre   | pop     | house       | ambient   | d&b      |

