.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, mirinda, sprite, tea
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, biathlon, climbing, golf
1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is golf is the person who's sport is golf##1
3. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
4. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's sport is golf is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3
6. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
7. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | mirinda     | hot-chocolate     | sprite          | tea |
| Sport      | skiing | biathlon | golf | climbing  |

 